Privacy Policy for Basket Bird

Last updated: 10.05.2024

This Privacy Policy describes the policies and procedures of Basket Bird on the collection, use, and disclosure of your information when you use the Basket Bird Game and tells you about your privacy rights and how the law protects you.

We respect your privacy, which is why we've ensured that no personal data is collected when you use our game.

1. No Data Collection

Basket Bird does not collect or store any personal data from our users. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it.

2. Information Use and Disclosure

Since we do not collect any personal data from our users, there's no information to use or disclose to third parties.

3. Ads in Game

Basket Bird contains ads. These ads are provided by third-party ad networks, which may use their own sets of information. However, these ad networks do not have access to personal data from the game, as we don't collect any. We encourage users to review the privacy policies of these third-party ad networks to get more information.

4. Support & Bug Reports

If you have any questions or experience any issues with Air Strike Hockey, please feel free to reach out to us:

On our Discord server: https://discord.gg/U99T8862CH
Via email at: brodoandcostudio@gmail.com
5. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. Changes are effective when they are posted on this page.

6. Your Consent to This Privacy Policy

By playing Basket Bird, you signify your acceptance of this policy. If you do not agree to this policy, please refrain from using our game.

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:

By visiting our Discord: https://discord.gg/U99T8862CH
By email: brodoandcostudio@gmail.com
Thank you for playing Basket Bird!
